Mexico ' s Gruma plans Europe tortilla plant . Gruma SA , the Mexican holding company for tortilla giant Grupo Industrial Maseca , plans to open a tortilla plant in Europe in the near future , a company director said Tuesday . " In the near future , we will have a tortilla plant in Europe , " Eduardo Sastre , director of communications , told a news conference . Sastre did not name the country that Gruma had earmarked for the tortilla plant or a specific timeframe . Tortillas are corn flour pancakes eaten more widely than bread in Mexico . ( ( - - Tomas de la Rosa , Mexico City newsroom + 525 728 7912 ) ) 
